00:01:47,900 --> 00:01:50,733
-Oh, quit torturing me, Kasumi.

5
00:01:50,833 --> 00:01:54,000
-It's not quite done yet,
so just leave it, OK?

6
00:01:54,100 --> 00:01:57,233
-But all I wanted was
an itty-bitty taste.

7
00:01:57,333 --> 00:01:59,600
KASUMI: I said no.

