AKANE (VOICEOVER):
"Into the Darkness."

12
00:02:13,833 --> 00:02:15,700
-This is so boring.

13
00:02:19,966 --> 00:02:22,766
[sighing]

14
00:02:22,866 --> 00:02:24,700
[boiling]

15
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,666
[sniffing]

