17
00:02:27,833 --> 00:02:31,533
Kasumi, is it ready yet?

18
00:02:31,633 --> 00:02:32,700
KASUMI: Not yet.

19
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,666
-Oh, nuts.

20
00:02:33,766 --> 00:02:43,066
