[snoring]

22
00:03:07,366 --> 00:03:08,000
-Here it is.

23
00:03:17,866 --> 00:03:19,833
And may your soul
now rest in peace.

24
00:03:19,933 --> 00:03:21,300
[music playing]

25
00:03:25,766 --> 00:03:27,100
[snoring]

26
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,733
WOMAN: Happosai.

27
00:03:32,833 --> 00:03:33,274
Happosai.

28
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:39,733
-Who are--

29
00:03:39,833 --> 00:03:42,466
-I am what you wished for.

30
00:03:42,566 --> 00:03:45,633
-Somebody pinch me cause
this can't be happening.

31
00:03:45,733 --> 00:03:48,300
-Here, I have bought
a gift for you.

32
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,266
-No, really-- well,
maybe just a taste.

33
00:03:54,533 --> 00:03:55,766
[laughing] Yes.

34
00:03:55,866 --> 00:03:56,307
Yes.

35
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,333
-Do I make you happy?

36
00:04:00,433 --> 00:04:01,766
[laughing]

37
00:04:03,333 --> 00:04:03,766
-Oh, yes.

38
00:04:03,866 --> 00:04:05,000
Oh, yes.

39
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:09,800
[laughing]

40
00:04:09,900 --> 00:04:11,233
-Hm?

41
00:04:11,333 --> 00:04:13,566
I wonder what the
freak's dreaming about.

42
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:21,833
Hey, taking a nap's
not a bad idea.

43
00:04:21,933 --> 00:04:25,033
[sniffing] Mm.

44
00:04:25,133 --> 00:04:26,500
[boiling]

45
00:04:30,433 --> 00:04:32,366
-Something smells good.

46
00:04:32,466 --> 00:04:33,766
[snoring]

47
